":"[fontSize:20]Even if my illness went away...@If I died, what would be the point?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp3.json","id":200301}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm preoccupied with my own safety@all the time, and that..."},{"chara":[{"id":200301}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That makes me feel so pitiful..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200301}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I can't be brave or strong like@you and Miss Tomoe. I just...can't."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"id":200301,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's why, I...!"},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Homura... I'm sorry. I didn't mean@to put pressure on you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But you don't have to worry anymore."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200101,"motion":201}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I became a Magical Girl..."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So I can protect the happiness@of people like you, you know?"},{"chara":[{"id":200301,"tear":1}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Kaname..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You can count on me to protect@this town!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
